        aria-labelledby="louver-composition-title"
      >
        <div class="container-lg">
          <div class="louver-composition__grid">
            <div class="louver-composition__content fade-up">
              <p class="louver-composition__eyebrow">(Engineered Material)</p>
              <h2
                class="louver-composition__title"
                id="louver-composition-title"
              >
                What Is a Pioneer PVC/WPC Interior Louver?
              </h2>
              <p>
                A premium fluted panel manufactured from Wood Plastic Composite
                and finished with a decorative PVC laminate. The engineered
                construction delivers the warmth of real wood with reliable
                resistance to water, termites, warping, and daily wear.
              </p>
              <p>
                Every profile is pre-finished, ready to install, easy to
                maintain, and developed for long-lasting wall and ceiling
                applications.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="louver-composition__visual fade-up" data-delay="160">
              <a
                class="louver-composition__image-link"
                href="assets/images/category/interior-louvers/about.png"
                data-lightbox-image
                aria-label="View full Pioneer PVC WPC interior louver profile image"
              >
